title: This YouTuber Stole From The Homeless...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Fidias, a channel that's been making the news in regards to his video where he travelled across Japan without paying for transit. I took a deeper dive on him and discovered he has a history of content where he has no regard for any law it seems. Thanks for watching!
